Description_lang: Your movement speed is increased by $s2% anytime you have not attacked for ${$s1/1000} sec.

description_blz.en_US: Your movement speed is increased by 30% anytime you have not attacked for 3 sec.
description_blz.es_MX: Aumenta tu velocidad de movimiento un 30% cada 3 s que no hayas atacado.
description_blz.pt_BR: A sua velocidade de movimento aumenta em 30% sempre que você ficar 3 s sem atacar.
description_blz.de_DE: Erhöht Eure Bewegungsgeschwindigkeit um 30%, wenn Ihr 3 Sek. lang nicht angreift.
description_blz.en_GB: Your movement speed is increased by 30% anytime you have not attacked for 3 sec.
description_blz.es_ES: Tu velocidad de movimiento aumentará un 30% cuando no hayas atacado durante 3 s.
description_blz.fr_FR: Votre vitesse de déplacement augmente de 30% à chaque fois que vous n’avez pas attaqué pendant une durée de 3 s.
description_blz.it_IT: Quando non si attacca nessuno per 3 s, la velocità di movimento aumenta del 30%.
description_blz.ru_RU: Если вы не атаковали в течение последних 3 сек., ваша скорость передвижения повышается на 30%.
description_blz.ko_KR: 3초 동안 공격을 하지 않으면 이동 속도가 30%만큼 증가합니다.
description_blz.zh_TW: 每當你停止攻擊3秒後，你的移動速度提高30%。
description_blz.zh_CN: 每当你有3秒不攻击时，会使你的移动速度提高30%。
